{"type": "article", "id": 3387, "title": "可变换角度放置的书架", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-10T07:44:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 7, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232729so5YdCqZFe8lQtxT.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t伦敦设计师 Sebastian Bergne 日前带来一款造型简洁的书架「Fiction Bookstand」，可调节为不同的角度使用，既可直立，亦可悬浮在半空中。当把书籍装满后，整个书架就像是被隐藏起来了一般。Fiction Bookstand 由一块折叠的钢板制成，被漆成纸白色，一个垂直面支撑放在架子上的书，另一个弯曲而成的面板则作为支撑架。Sebastian Bergne 表示自己想创造一些令人意想不到的东西，比如用不同的方式来展示书籍。定价 78 英镑，<a href=\"http://www.sebastianbergne.com/product/fiction/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"http://static.dezeen.com/uploads/2014/11/Fiction-bookstand-by-Sebastian-Bergne_dezeen_sq.gif\" width=\"640\" alt=\"\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232727BOjSdqgZ9PhlcGur.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052327284HswbkVctZ9C5KOE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232728x8FnihQX0ZNBaERe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232728v6LFzSWdIlapnRZb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}